title: Eco-friendly Urban Living - Victorian Downtown Mpls
posting_body: ['Available 11/1/2022', 'Turn of the century beautiful Victorian house Just south of downtown Minneapolis, only 8 blocks from US bank stadium, with easy access to multiple metro transit bus lines, coffee shops, music venues, restaurants, and bars, this cozy 1 bedroom unit includes FREE:', '- Wifi ($50/month value)', '- Water', '- Trash & compost', '- Off-street parking space (additional fee)', '- laundry', '- Gym access', '- Locally made soaps (laundry, personal soaps, tub and tile)', '- Metal, textile, lighting, electronics, plastic bag, styrofoam recycling', '- On counter composter and compost bags', '- Eco-friendly toilet paper, LED light bulbs, and compostable dog waste bags', 'To learn more about us, view availability, or schedule a showing visit: <URL>', 'Utilities paid by tenant:', 'Electricity', 'Gas', 'Utilities paid by owner:', 'Water', 'Trash & Compost', 'Internet', 'This property is pet friendly!', 'Both cats and dogs allowed pending owner approval, along with pet rent/deposit.', 'Off-street parking available behind building.', 'Garden spaces available for reservation at neighboring community garden for an additional one time fee.', 'To learn more about us, view availability, or schedule a showing visit: <URL>', 'Green Rock Apartments:', 'Green Rock Apartments is a small property management firm focused on eco-conscious urban living.', 'We have been in operation since 1991.', 'Our mission is to provide safe, comfortable, and eco-friendly living spaces that foster healthy, sustainable communities.', 'To learn more about us, view availability, or schedule a showing visit: <URL>']
